text: Gumbrechtshoffen is a commune which is in Grand Est in the Bas-Rhin department in northeast France. It is northwest of Haguenau. == Geography == The commune is placed between Niederbronn and Haguenau, a couple of kilometres to the west of the main road that connects the two. It is traversed by the river Zinsel. == References == Category:Communes in Bas-Rhin
title: Gumbrechtshoffen
